  The famous ambiguous pair at n=7:
    bits=4728: Ps=-13, |Ps|=13, pop=6, (-1)^pop=+1, H=109
    bits=4658: Ps=-19, |Ps|=19, pop=5, (-1)^pop=-1, H=111

  These have |Ps|=13 vs |Ps|=19 — DIFFERENT magnitudes!
